House Resolution 893
By: Representatives Scott of the 76th, Schofield of the 63rd, and Davis of the 87th
A RESOLUTION
1 Commending Aretha Sharice Hopkins, Toney Elementary School's 2024-2025 Teacher of
2 the Year; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, nothing is more vital to the future of our state than the education of our young
4 people, and Aretha Sharice Hopkins exemplifies the selfless dedication that is characteristic
5 of our finest teachers; and
6 WHEREAS, Aretha Sharice Hopkins is a highly praised educator at Toney Elementary
7 School in Decatur, Georgia, tirelessly directing an extraordinary amount of time and talent
8 toward guiding students to a brighter future; and
9 WHEREAS, Aretha Sharice Hopkins has earned distinction and numerous awards for
10 teaching excellence as a result of her dedication to her students and her profession and has
11 been honored as Toney Elementary School's 2024-2025 Teacher of the Year; and
12 WHEREAS, in recognition of such remarkable contributions to the education and welfare
13 of Georgia's students, it is abundantly fitting and proper for this body to honor the
14 extraordinary accomplishments and academic achievements of this outstanding educator.
